quran[7{c,v,t}:
7,31,"ae bani aadam, har ibadat ke mauqa par apni zeenat se aaraasta raho aur khao piyo aur hadd se tajawaz nah karo, Allah hadd se bherne walon ko pasand nahi karta"
7,32,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho kis ne Allah ki uss zeenat ko haraam kar diya jisay Allah ne apne bundon ke liye nikala tha aur kis ne khuda ki bakhsh hui pak cheeze mamnoo kar den? kaho, yeh saari cheeze duniya ki zindagi mein bhi imaan laane walon ke liye hain, aur qayamat ke roz to khalstan unhi ke liye hon gi iss terhan hum apni baatein saaf saaf bayan karte hain unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhnay walay hain"
7,33,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho ke mere rab ne jo cheeze haraam ki hain woh to yeh hain : be sharmi ke kaam khuwa khulay hon ya chupay aur gunah aur haq ke khilaaf zayad-ti aur yeh ke Allah ke sath tum kisi ko shareek karo jis ke liye uss ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki aur yeh ke Allah ke naam par koi aisi baat kaho jis ke mutaliq tumhe ilm nah ho ke woh haqeeqat mein isi ne farmai hai"
7,34,"har qoum ke liye mohlat ki aik muddat muqarrar hai, phir jab kisi qoum ki muddat aan poori hoti hai to aik gharri bhar ki takheer o taqdeem bhi nahi hoti"
7,35,"( aur yeh baat Allah ne aaghaz takhleeq hi mein saaf farma di thi ke ) ae bani aadam, yaad rakho, agar tumahray paas khud tum hi mein se aisay rasool ayen jo tumhe meri ayaat suna rahay hon, to jo koi nafarmani se bachay ga aur apne rawayya ki islaah kar le ga is ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai"
7,36,aur jo log hamari ayaat kojjhutlainge aur un ke muqaabla mein sar kashi barten ge wohi ahal dozakh hon ge jahan woh hamesha rahen ge
7,37,"zahir hai ke uss se bara zalim aur ko noon ho ga jo bilkul jhooti baatein ghurr kar Allah ki taraf mansoob kere ya Allah ki sachhi ayaat kojhutla-ay aisay log apne noshta taqdeer ke mutabiq apna hissa paate rahen ge, yahan taq ke woh gharri aa jaye gi jab hamaray beje hue farishtay un ki roohein qabz karne ke liye pohnchain ge uss waqt woh unn se poucheen ge ke batao, ab kahan hain tumahray woh mabood jin ko tum ko khuda ke bajaye pkarte thay? woh kahin ge ke,"" sab hum se gum ho gay"" aur woh khud apne khilaaf gawahi den ge ke hum waqai munkir haq thay"
